	$(document).on('click','.saveListing',function(e){

<!--Validate Form and Loading button-->	  
<script>
  $(document).ready(function(){
	  $.validator.addClassRules("requiredS", { 
		required: true,
		  normalizer: function(value) {
			return $.trim(value);
		  }
	  });
	  $.validator.addClassRules("confirmPw", { 
		minlength : 5,
		equalTo : "#password",
		required: function(element){
			return $("#password").val()!="";
		}
	  });
	  $.validator.addClassRules("password", { 
		minlength : 5,
	  });
		$('button[type="submit"]:not(.noVal)').click(function(e){
			var button = $(this);
			var form = $(this).closest("form");

			$(form).validate({
    			ignore: ':hidden:not(.do-not-ignore)',
				errorClass: "text-danger small d-block",
    			errorElement : 'span',
				errorPlacement: function(error, element) {
				  var form = $(element).parents('form');
				  if (form.hasClass("animate-form-labels") || $(element).attr("id") == "agree_privacy" || element.parent().hasClass("has-float-label")) {
					$(element).closest(".form-group").append(error)
				  }else {
					error.insertAfter(element);
				  }
				}
			});
			if($(form).valid()){
				$(form).submit();
				$(button).prop("disabled",true);
				$(button).html("<i class='fas fa-circle-notch fa-spin'></i> loading...");
			}
		});
	});

</script>	
<script>
	const queryString = window.location.search;
	const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(queryString);
	const searched = urlParams.get('s');
	const stateCookie = getCookie("state");
	const countryCookie = getCookie("country");

	$(document).ready(function(){
		if(!searched){
			if(stateCookie && countryCookie)
				getListings(stateCookie,countryCookie);
			else
				initLocation();
		}else{
			completeSetup();
		}
		
	});
	function paginate(){
		var pageParts = $(".paginate");
		var numPages = pageParts.length;
		var perPage = 10;

		pageParts.slice(perPage).hide();
		
		
		$("#page-nav-results").pagination({
			items: numPages,
			itemsOnPage: perPage,
			cssStyle: "light-theme",
			onPageClick: function(pageNum) {
				var start = perPage * (pageNum - 1);
				var end = start + perPage;
				pageParts.hide()
						 .slice(start, end).show();

				$("html, body").animate({
					scrollTop: 300
					}, 600);
				return false;

			}
		});
	}
	function loadImages(){
		const observer = lozad(); 
		observer.observe();
	}
	const successfulLookup = position => {
	  const { latitude, longitude } = position.coords;
	  fetch(`https://api.opencagedata.com/geocode/v1/json?q=${latitude}+${longitude}&key=8427aefc6eba4813b04fc6633d76ff77`)
		.then(response => response.json())
		.then(data => {
			console.log(data);
		  	let state = data["results"][0]["components"]["state"];
		  	let country = data["results"][0]["components"]["country"];
		  	setCookie("state", state, 7);
		  	setCookie("country", country, 7);
			getListings(state,country);
		});

	}
	function getListings(state,country){
		let stateEl = document.getElementById("state");
		let countryEl = document.getElementById("country");
		stateEl.value = state;
		countryEl.value = country;
		$.ajax({
			url: "/includes/get_listings_list.php",
			dataType: 'html',
			type: 'post',
			data: {state: state,country: country,hideIntro: 1},
			success: function(data) {
				$("#resultList").html(data);
				completeSetup();
			}
		});
	}
	function completeSetup(){
		paginate();
		loadImages();
	}
	function initLocation(){
		if (window.navigator.geolocation) {
			window.navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(successfulLookup, completeSetup);
		}  
	}
	function setCookie(cname, cvalue, exdays) {
	  const d = new Date();
	  d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays*24*60*60*1000));
	  let expires = "expires="+ d.toUTCString();
	  document.cookie = cname + "=" + cvalue + ";" + expires + ";path=/";
	}
	function getCookie(cname) {
	  let name = cname + "=";
	  let decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
	  let ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
	  for(let i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
		let c = ca[i];
		while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
		  c = c.substring(1);
		}
		if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
		  return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
		}
	  }
	  return "";
	}


</script>
